milestones.description: Waqas Barkat and Anshy Rath's 60-run partnership is HKG's highest for the 2nd wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 45 between Tabarak Dar and Atkinson
Atkinson and Anshy Rath's 54-run partnership is HKG's highest for the 3rd wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 50 between French and Tabarak Dar
Aizaz Khan and Babar Hayat's 66-run partnership is HKG's highest for the 6th wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 34 between Babar Hayat and Ankur Vasishta
Babar Hayat and Haseeb Amjad's 50-run partnership is HKG's highest for the 7th wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 29 between Haseeb Amjad and Ankur Vasishta
Assad Vala and Tony Ura's 8-run partnership is PNG's highest for the 1st wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 3 between Assad Vala and Tony Ura
Tony Ura and Lega Siaka's 41-run partnership is PNG's highest for the 2nd wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 35 between Assad Vala and Lega Siaka
Geraint Jones and Lega Siaka's 65-run partnership is PNG's highest for the 3rd wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 28 between Geraint Jones and Lega Siaka
Vani Morea and Lega Siaka's 87-run partnership is PNG's highest for the 4th wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 6 between Geraint Jones and Vani Morea
Mahuru Dai and Vani Morea's 23-run partnership is PNG's highest for the 5th wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 4 between Mahuru Dai and Vani Morea
Willie Gavera has become the top wicket-taker for PNG in ODIs with 4 wickets, going past Assad Vala's 2
Vani Morea has scored 2 fifty-plus scores in ODIs, the most for PNG breaking Charles Amini's record
Lega Siaka has become the top scorer for PNG in ODIs with 140 runs, going past Charles Amini's 61
Assad Vala has broken the record for most catches (2) in ODIs for PNG, going past Charles Amini's 1
Lega Siaka has broken the record for most sixes (3) in ODIs for PNG, going past Vani Morea's 1
Lega Siaka has broken the record for most runs in boundaries (48) in an innings in ODIs for PNG, going past Charles Amini's 32
Haseeb Amjad has broken the record for most sixes in an innings (4) in ODIs for HKG, going past Irfan Ahmed's 2
Lega Siaka has broken the record for most sixes in an innings (2) in ODIs for PNG, going past Vani Morea's 1
This is the highest match aggregate (525) involving teams Hong Kong & P.N.G. in ODIs
Lega Siaka's 109 is the highest individual score in ODIs (for PNG), surpassing Charles Amini's 61
Lega Siaka has broken the record for most catches in an innings (2) in ODIs for PNG, going past Charles Amini's 1
Aizaz Khan and Babar Hayat's 66-run partnership is HKG's highest for any wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 60 between Irfan Ahmed and Skhawat Ali
Norman Vanua has conceded the most runs in an innings (60) in ODIs for PNG, going past Mahuru Dai's record of 43
Babar Hayat has scored 2 fifty-plus scores in ODIs, the most for HKG breaking Atkinson's record
Charles Amini has broken the record for playing the most ODIs (2) for PNG, going past Chris Amini
